videos.description: Saddiq Bey puts back a big dunk for Villanova as it leads No. 1 Kansas early.
videos.headline: Bey throws down big putback dunk

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick drops a 3-pointer to get Allen Fieldhouse hyped in the first half vs. Villanova.
videos.headline: Vick ignites The Phog with 3

videos.description: Eric Paschall gets a big and-1 for Villanova in the second half on a simple, but slick pivot move.
videos.headline: Paschall gets and-1 on slick pivot move

videos.description: Dedric Lawson hits a jumper to put Kansas up by 5 late in the second half as the hometown crowd goes crazy.
videos.headline: Lawson's big-time jumper puts Kansas up

videos.description: Villanova's Phil Booth throws down a huge one-handed slam late in the second half.
videos.headline: Booth throws down monster slam
